## üìã Phase 1: Multi-Tenant MVP (6 Weeks)

### Week 1: Database & Authentication Setup

#### Backend Tasks
- [ ] **Day 1-2**: Project initialization
  - Initialize Node.js project with Express
  - Set up TypeScript configuration
  - Install dependencies (express, prisma, bcrypt, jsonwebtoken, etc.)
  - Configure environment variables (.env)
  
- [ ] **Day 3-4**: Database schema
  - Create Prisma schema with Tenants, Users, MenuItems, Categories tables
  - Run migrations
  - Seed database with test data
  
- [ ] **Day 5**: Authentication system
  - Implement JWT token generation/validation
  - Create auth middleware
  - Build password hashing utilities

#### Deliverables
- ‚úÖ Database schema created and migrated
- ‚úÖ Authentication utilities ready
- ‚úÖ Project structure established

---

### Week 2: Core Backend APIs

#### Backend Tasks
- [ ] **Day 1-2**: Tenant registration API
  - POST /api/auth/register endpoint
  - Slug generation logic
  - Email validation
  - Create tenant + admin user in transaction
  
- [ ] **Day 3**: Authentication APIs
  - POST /api/auth/login
  - POST /api/auth/logout
  - GET /api/auth/me
  - POST /api/auth/refresh
  
- [ ] **Day 4-5**: Tenant management APIs
  - GET /api/tenants/:id
  - PUT /api/tenants/:id
  - GET /api/tenants/slug/:slug
  - Tenant middleware (inject tenant context)

#### Deliverables
- ‚úÖ Registration flow working
- ‚úÖ Login/logout functional
- ‚úÖ Tenant CRUD operations complete

---

### Week 3: Menu Management Backend

#### Backend Tasks
