## üéØ MVP Success Checklist

### Core Functionality
- [ ] Hotel can register with email/password
- [ ] Hotel gets unique slug (e.g., "hotel-paradise")
- [ ] Hotel can upload logo and set brand color
- [ ] Hotel can add/edit/delete menu items
- [ ] Hotel can upload menu item images
- [ ] Hotel can organize items by category
- [ ] Hotel can toggle item availability
- [ ] Hotel can download QR code (PNG format)
- [ ] Customer can scan QR and view menu
- [ ] Customer sees hotel's branding (logo, colors)
- [ ] Customer can add items to cart
- [ ] Customer can checkout via WhatsApp
- [ ] WhatsApp message includes order details and hotel's number

### Technical Requirements
- [ ] Multi-tenant data isolation working
- [ ] Authentication secure (JWT, bcrypt)
- [ ] File uploads working (images, logos)
- [ ] PWA installable on mobile
- [ ] Responsive design (mobile-first)
- [ ] HTTPS enabled
- [ ] Database backups configured
- [ ] Error logging implemented

### Documentation
- [ ] README with setup instructions
- [ ] API documentation
- [ ] User guide for hotel admins
- [ ] Deployment guide

