## üì¶ Dependencies to Install

### Backend
```bash
npm install express cors dotenv
npm install @prisma/client
npm install bcrypt jsonwebtoken
npm install multer
npm install qrcode
npm install slugify
npm install joi  # or zod for validation

npm install -D prisma typescript @types/node @types/express
npm install -D @types/bcrypt @types/jsonwebtoken @types/multer
npm install -D nodemon ts-node
```

### Frontend
```bash
npm create vite@latest frontend -- --template react-ts
cd frontend
npm install react-router-dom
npm install zustand
npm install axios
npm install react-hook-form
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init -p
```

---

## üîß Environment Variables

### Backend (.env)
```env
# Server
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

# Database
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/qrmenu"

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-key-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=15m
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your-refresh-secret
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# File Upload
MAX_FILE_SIZE=5242880  # 5MB
UPLOAD_DIR=./uploads

# Frontend URL (for CORS)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Platform
PLATFORM_DOMAIN=yourdomain.com
```

### Frontend (.env)
```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
VITE_PLATFORM_NAME=QR Menu Platform
```

---

## üöÄ Quick Start Commands

### Development
```bash
# Backend
cd backend
npm install
npx prisma migrate dev
npm run dev

# Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Production Deployment
```bash
# Backend
cd backend
npm install --production
npx prisma migrate deploy
pm2 start dist/app.js --name qrmenu-api

# Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm run build
# Copy dist/ to /var/www/qrmenu/
```

