## üìä Testing Checklist

### Manual Testing Scenarios

#### Scenario 1: Hotel Registration
1. Visit landing page
2. Click "Get Started"
3. Fill registration form
4. Submit
5. Verify redirect to dashboard
6. Verify slug generated correctly
7. Verify QR code created

#### Scenario 2: Menu Management
1. Login as hotel admin
2. Navigate to menu items
3. Click "Add Item"
4. Fill form with image
5. Submit
6. Verify item appears in list
7. Edit item
8. Delete item

#### Scenario 3: Customer Order
1. Scan QR code (or visit /{slug})
2. Verify hotel branding displayed
3. Browse menu items
4. Add items to cart
5. View cart
6. Click "Order via WhatsApp"
7. Verify WhatsApp opens with correct message

